pre-Adamite
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:an early name for settlers who had arrived in what was to become Canterbury before the `Pilgrim' settlers (e.g. the Deans)
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: noun and adjective uses
